metadata.title: Bell 407
aws::graph::propositions: Military Operators of the Bell 407 Helicopter
Argentina operates the Bell 407 through the Argentine Air Force.
Argentina operates the Bell 407 through the Argentine Army.
Bangladesh operates the Bell 407 through the Rapid Action Battalion.
Guatemala operates the Bell 407 through the Guatemalan Air Force.
Iraq operates the Bell 407 through the Iraqi Army.
Jamaica operates the Bell 407 through the Jamaica Defence Force.
Mexico operates the Bell 407 through the Mexican Air Force.
Nepal operates the Bell 407 through the Nepalese Army Air Service.
Panama operates the Bell 407 through the National Aeronaval Service.
United Arab Emirates operates the Bell 407 through the United Arab Emirates Air Force.
United States operates the Bell 407 through the United States Army.
The United States Army operates 5 units of the Bell 407.
